{"tid":1779931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日俾人話你「好靜 好少野講」？","createTime":"2019-12-12T04:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T19:32:56.000Z","uid":151451,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fabf92cd12172aaed7d0099664b42cee465150d9","tid":1779931,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"由細到大都俾人話好靜好少野講<br />\n小學中學見家長班主任一定會同我講呢句<br />\n<br />\n近排返新工識到新同事 臨放工前又問我<br />\n「點解你咁靜嘅 平時都無乜野講㗎」<br />\n但明明我已經同佢有傾有講 我又分享吓我自己野咁<br />\n<br />\n只係覺得 有時無話題咪靜靜地唔出聲算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實點先算多野講？就算無野講都要夾硬搵野嚟講？<br />\n利伸毒撚"},{"pid":"5cc9bd4d0f603b15b8e3a5739028066324ca5c42","tid":1779931,"uid":133277,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n次次人地問我都心諗同你冇野好講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30d8ec8cf727ad3baa6a9ebba6d1f235d86995d","tid":1779931,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:13:53.000Z","msg":"你咪話關你9事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62a5d10079b3cd7482249ee11dc2656ca3146da","tid":1779931,"uid":192528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"毒撚圍爐區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144e959b5f67797016af1527837088c9bfb51471","tid":1779931,"uid":39470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"多野講咪又有人話你好煩<br />\n<br />\n使乜理人太多"},{"pid":"9321d85f3290dfbea2bac208527594d8570d783b","tid":1779931,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"唔係少嘢講既，不過大家興趣唔同冇咩共同話題姐"},{"pid":"4d76d336ceafc23f02b55dde6d4370592f5092f9","tid":1779931,"uid":82717,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"間唔中會有人咁講<br />\n工作嘅時候會迫自己講多啲 唔可以太靜唔出聲"},{"pid":"c5af94cfff543ac5918842cabbafde3fb58fa14c","tid":1779931,"uid":7